      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/92/2",
      "text": [
        " : سُئِلَ أَبُو عَبْدِ اَللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ مِنْ أَيْنَ يُجَرَّدُ اَلصِّبْيَانُ فَقَالَ «كَانَ أَبِي عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ يُجَرِّدُهُمْ مِنْ فَخٍّ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2894 - It was narrated from Ayyub, the brother of Udaym, who said:\nAbu Abdullah (as) was asked: \"From where are the children stripped (for Ihram)?\"\nImam (as) said: \"My father (as) used to strip them at Fakh.\""
        ]
      }
    },
